This project is made to run solr's tutorial.

For now it works on linux and mac, but feel free to make further changes.

TODO: license data

1) Start it up:	mvn clean compile install tomcat7:run
2) Reindex bars data: http://localhost:8080/solr-search/restaurantcore/dataimport?command=full-import&clean=true&wt=json
3) Go: http://localhost:8080/solr-search/admin


Examples:
* Query all - http://localhost:8080/solr-search/restaurantcore/select?q=*%3A*&fl=score,*&wt=json
* Simple sort by popularity - http://localhost:8080/solr-search/restaurantcore/select?q=*%3A*&fl=score,*&wt=json&sort=rating%20desc
* Function query for single females
** As a sort - http://localhost:8080/solr-search/restaurantcore/select?q=*%3A*&fl=score,*&wt=json&sort=product(female,%20unmarried)%20desc
** As a score - http://localhost:8080/solr-search/restaurantcore/select?q={!func}product(female,%20unmarried)&fl=score,*&wt=json
** TODO: As a boost query
